\section{Introduction}

The {\Tt{}netdraw\nwendquote} module provides an interface for drawing
netlist objects.  This module is even more in flux than most,
since beside beams I'm uncertain what I'll need to draw.


\section{Interface}

\nwfilename{netdraw.nw}\nwbegincode{1}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}}\moddef{netdraw.h~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}}\endmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwenddeflinemarkup

\nwnotused{netdraw.h}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{2}\nwdocspar

The {\Tt{}line\nwendquote} method draws a line between two points in the
three-dimensional coordinate system in which the device lives.
In general, the {\Tt{}line\nwendquote} method will need to do some sort of
transformation to get to a coordinate system appropriate for
projection to the screen.  There is no default {\Tt{}line\nwendquote}
implementation.

\nwalsodefined{\\{NW1ZXxII-44Zsg-2}\\{NW1ZXxII-44Zsg-3}\\{NW1ZXxII-44Zsg-4}}\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{6}\nwdocspar

The {\Tt{}plane\nwendquote} method draws a (planar) surface specified by a set
of points.  The default {\Tt{}plane\nwendquote} implementation uses the 
{\Tt{}line\nwendquote} method to draw a wire frame.

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{7}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-2}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-2}}}\moddef{\code{}netdraw\edoc{} functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-1}{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-3}\nwenddeflinemarkup

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{10}\nwdocspar

The {\Tt{}beam\nwendquote} function draws a deformed beam shape.  The default
{\Tt{}beam\nwendquote} implementation uses the {\Tt{}plane\nwendquote} method to do most
of the drawing. 
The {\Tt{}beam\nwendquote} function takes a transformation from local to global coordinates,
the length, width, and height parameters for the beam, and a vector of
variable identifiers (there should be twelve of them).

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{11}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-3}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-3}}}\moddef{\code{}netdraw\edoc{} functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-1MHJsH-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-2}{NW1ZXxII-bGrh8-4}\nwenddeflinemarkup

The {\Tt{}get{\_}x\nwendquote} function gets a pointer to the displacement vector to be
used in the call by the default {\Tt{}beam\nwendquote} function (and possibly some
other future default functions).

\section{Implementation}

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{19}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}}\moddef{netdraw.c~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}}\endmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwenddeflinemarkup

#include <netdraw.h>

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{21}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\moddef{functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\endmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{\relax}{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-2}\nwenddeflinemarkup
void netdraw_line(netdraw_gc_t* gc, double* x1, double* x2)
\{
    assert(gc->methods->line);
    gc->methods->line(gc->data, x1, x2);
\}

void netdraw_line_xyz(netdraw_gc_t* gc,
                              double x1, double y1, double z1,
                              double x2, double y2, double z2)
\{
    double p1[3], p2[3];
    p1[0] = x1, p1[1] = y1, p1[2] = z1;
    p2[0] = x2, p2[1] = y2, p2[2] = z2;
    netdraw_line(gc, p1, p2);
\}

\nwalsodefined{\\{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-2}\\{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-3}\\{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-4}\\{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-5}}\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{22}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{23}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-2}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-2}}}\moddef{functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-3}\nwenddeflinemarkup
void netdraw_plane(netdraw_gc_t* gc, double* xpts, int npts)
\{
    if (gc->methods->plane) \{
        gc->methods->plane(gc->data, xpts, npts);
    \} else \{
        int i;
        netdraw_line(gc, xpts, xpts + 3*(npts-1));
        for (i = 0; i < npts-1; ++i) \{
            netdraw_line(gc, xpts, xpts + 3);
            xpts += 3;
        \}
    \}
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{24}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{25}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-3}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-3}}}\moddef{functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-2}{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-4}\nwenddeflinemarkup
void netdraw_plane_quad(netdraw_gc_t* gc, 
                                double* x1, double* x2,
                                double* x3, double* x4)
\{
    double pts[12];
    memcpy(pts + 0, x1, 3*sizeof(double));
    memcpy(pts + 3, x2, 3*sizeof(double));
    memcpy(pts + 6, x3, 3*sizeof(double));
    memcpy(pts + 9, x4, 3*sizeof(double));
    netdraw_plane(gc, pts, 4);
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{26}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{27}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1VvxMr-1}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1VvxMr-1}}}\moddef{macros~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1VvxMr-1}}}\endmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwenddeflinemarkup
#define get_disp(i) \\
    ((x == NULL || vindex == NULL || vindex[i] < 0) ? 0 : x[vindex[i]])

#define NPTS 10

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{28}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{29}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-4}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-4}}}\moddef{functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-3}{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-5}\nwenddeflinemarkup
void netdraw_beam(netdraw_gc_t* gc, double* transform,
                          double l, double w, double h, int* vindex)
\{
    if (gc->methods->beam) \{
        gc->methods->beam(gc->data, transform, l, w, h, vindex);
    \} else \{
        double* x = netdraw_get_x(gc);
        double xlocal[12];
        double pts[NPTS*12];

        beam_get_local(transform, xlocal, x, vindex);
        beam_points(pts, l, w, h, xlocal, transform);
        beam_draw(gc, pts);
    \}
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{30}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{31}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}}}\moddef{static functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}}}\endmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{\relax}{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-2}\nwenddeflinemarkup
static void beam_get_local(double* transform, double* xlocal, 
                           double* x, int* vindex)
\{
    int i;

    for (i = 0; i < 12; ++i)
        xlocal[i] = get_disp(i);

    for (i = 0; i < 12; i += 3)
        affine_apply_AT(transform, &(xlocal[i]));
\}

\nwalsodefined{\\{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-2}\\{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-3}\\{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-4}}\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{32}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{33}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-2}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-2}}}\moddef{static functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-3}\nwenddeflinemarkup
static void hermite(double* f, int stride, double L, int n,
                    double f0, double f00, double fL, double fLL)
\{
    double f0L   = ( fL   - f0   ) / L;
    double f00L  = ( f0L  - f00  ) / L;
    double f0LL  = ( fLL  - f0L  ) / L;
    double f00LL = ( f0LL - f00L ) / L;
    int i;

    for (i = 0; i < n; ++i) \{
        double s = i*L / (n-1);
        *f = f0 + s*(f00 + s*(f00L + (s-L)*f00LL));
        f += stride;
    \}
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{34}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{35}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-3}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-3}}}\moddef{static functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-2}{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-4}\nwenddeflinemarkup
static void beam_points(double* pts, double l, double w, double h, 
                        double* x, double* transform)
\{
    double x1  = x[0], y1  = x[1],  z1  = x[2];
    double x2  = x[6], y2  = x[7],  z2  = x[8];
    double             ry1 = x[4],  rz1 = x[5];
    double             ry2 = x[10], rz2 = x[11];

    double rotx1[12];
    double rotx2[12];
    double A[12], *Ap = A;
    double B[12], *Bp = B;

    int i, j;

    A[0] = 0; A[1]  =  w/2;  A[2]  = -h/2;
    A[3] = 0; A[4]  =  w/2;  A[5]  =  h/2;
    A[6] = 0; A[7]  = -w/2;  A[8]  =  h/2;
    A[9] = 0; A[10] = -w/2;  A[11] = -h/2;
    memcpy(B, A, 12*sizeof(double));

    affine_identity (rotx1);
    affine_identity (rotx2);
    affine_rotate_ox(rotx1, ry1);
    affine_rotate_ox(rotx2, ry2);

    for (i = 0; i < 4; ++i) \{
        affine_apply(rotx1, Ap);
        affine_apply(rotx2, Bp);
        for (j = 0; j < NPTS; ++j) 
            pts[j*12] = ((NPTS-1-j)*(Ap[0]+x1) + (j)*(Bp[0]+x2+l)) / (NPTS-1);
        hermite(pts+1, 12, l, NPTS,  Ap[1]+y1,  rz1, Bp[1]+y2,    rz2);
        hermite(pts+2, 12, l, NPTS,  Ap[2]+z1, -ry1, Bp[2]+z2,   -ry2);
        Ap  += 3;
        Bp  += 3;
        pts += 3;
    \}

    pts -= 12;
    for (i = 0; i < 12*NPTS; i += 3) \{
        affine_apply(transform, pts + i);
    \}
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{36}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{37}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-4}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-4}}}\moddef{static functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-1duChy-3}{\relax}\nwenddeflinemarkup
static void beam_draw(netdraw_gc_t* gc, double* pts)
\{
    int i, j;

    /* Draw end caps */
    netdraw_plane(gc, pts, 4);
    netdraw_plane(gc, pts + 12*(NPTS-1), 4);

    /* Draw exterior of each segment */
    for (i = 1; i < NPTS; ++i) \{
        for (j = 0; j < 12; j += 3) \{
            int ix1 = (j+0) % 12;
            int ix2 = (j+3) % 12;
            netdraw_plane_quad(gc, 
                               &pts[ix1], &pts[ix1 + 12],
                               &pts[ix2 + 12], &pts[ix2]);
        \}
        pts += 12;
    \}
\}

\nwused{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwendcode{}\nwbegindocs{38}\nwdocspar

\nwenddocs{}\nwbegincode{39}\sublabel{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-5}\nwmargintag{{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-5}}}\moddef{functions~{\nwtagstyle{}\subpageref{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-1}}}\plusendmoddef\nwstartdeflinemarkup\nwusesondefline{\\{NW1ZXxII-40lrkf-1}}\nwprevnextdefs{NW1ZXxII-nRuDO-4}{\relax}\nwenddeflinemarkup
double* netdraw_get_x(netdraw_gc_t* gc)
\{
    if (gc->methods->get_x) \{
        return gc->methods->get_x(gc->data);
    \} else \{
        return NULL;
    \}
\}
